    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:0",
      "text": "让我们在 Solaris 中扮演 cinematographer（摄影指导），并学习 Pixar 的 lighting toolset。",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:2",
      "text": "灯光基础课程（Light Basics）",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:3",
      "text": "Light Intensity（灯光强度）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:4",
      "text": "了解关于 light intensity 和 exposure 基本概念的 Pixar-centric workflows。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:5",
      "text": "Light Temperature（灯光色温）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:6",
      "text": "学习用于匹配 incandescent light color 的最基础 lighting attributes 之一。",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:7",
      "text": "Normalize Light（灯光归一化）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:8",
      "text": "暂时放下 physics！学习如何通过 light normalization 为 lighting 和 shadows 带来更多艺术控制。",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:9",
      "text": "Diffuse & Specular（漫反射与高光）",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:10",
      "text": "通过分别控制 diffuse 和 specular light contributions，进一步打破物理规则。",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:11",
      "text": "Intensity Near Distance（近距离强度）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:13",
      "text": "Light Types（灯光类型）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:15",
      "text": "穹顶灯课程（Dome Light）",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:16",
      "text": "dome 或 environment light 是每个 photorealistic render 中的基础灯光，因此我们来看看它的 basics。",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:17",
      "text": "Rectangular Light（矩形灯）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:18",
      "text": "了解 lighter 工具箱中最常用的工具……Pixar Rectangular Light。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:19",
      "text": "圆柱灯课程（Cylinder Light）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:20",
      "text": "Strip Lights 和 Lightsabers 有一个共同点……Cylinder Lights！",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:21",
      "text": "球形灯课程（Sphere Lights）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:23",
      "text": "Light Filters 基础课程（Light Filters Basics）",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:24",
      "text": "学习 Light Filters……这是 Pixar 进行创意 lighting 的秘密配方！",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:25",
      "text": "Light Filter Basics（灯光过滤器基础）",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8aaffac852:26",
      "text": "Eugene Riecansky 会在 Solaris 中介绍强大的 light filter toolset。",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    }
  ],
